313
00:18:23,430 --> 00:18:24,640
Her aunt, who adopted her,

314
00:18:24,640 --> 00:18:26,240
was used by Cao Mang.

315
00:18:26,270 --> 00:18:26,990
She,

316
00:18:27,010 --> 00:18:29,070
on the other hand, is being used by Cao Mang

317
00:18:29,070 --> 00:18:31,070
while also being manipulated by us.

318
00:18:31,220 --> 00:18:33,490
She is not a pawn in court struggles.

319
00:18:33,510 --> 00:18:35,940
She is a living, breathing person.

320
00:18:36,270 --> 00:18:38,130
But she tried to kill your brother

321
00:18:38,270 --> 00:18:39,660
and even tried to harm you.

322
00:18:39,660 --> 00:18:43,220
It would be strange if she didn't seek revenge against the Yue family.

323
00:18:43,220 --> 00:18:44,140
Her father and brothers

324
00:18:44,140 --> 00:18:46,430
died in the battle at Dayan Pass.

325
00:18:46,590 --> 00:18:48,980
