332
00:18:58,510 --> 00:19:00,880
and some never saw another sunrise?

333
00:19:01,110 --> 00:19:03,770
Although our Yue family wasn't the mastermind,

334
00:19:04,550 --> 00:19:06,410
we bear the main responsibility.

335
00:19:07,270 --> 00:19:08,070
Ling'er,

336
00:19:09,450 --> 00:19:12,390
someone as unclear-headed as Consort Hui

337
00:19:12,590 --> 00:19:13,830
should not remain in the palace.

338
00:19:13,830 --> 00:19:14,950
I disagree.

339
00:19:15,940 --> 00:19:16,590
Yingying.

340
00:19:16,590 --> 00:19:17,790
Qu.

341
00:19:18,700 --> 00:19:19,510
Hurry up and hold her.

342
00:19:19,510 --> 00:19:20,420
Yingying.

343
00:19:22,420 --> 00:19:23,440
Yingying.

344
00:19:24,140 --> 00:19:25,700
Yingying, are you alright?

345
00:19:25,870 --> 00:19:27,270
