Judging by the placement of these bamboo poles,

577
00:30:51,960 --> 00:30:54,820
they seem to be using the Eight Trigrams Formation.

578
00:31:07,430 --> 00:31:10,160
Wanna trap me with the Eight Trigrams Formation?

579
00:31:10,560 --> 00:31:12,000
Such a trivial trick.

580
00:31:12,380 --> 00:31:15,370
Heaven by three continuous lines; Earth by six broken lines.
Thunder like an upturned bowl.

581
00:31:15,370 --> 00:31:17,480
Mountain like an overturned bowl. Fire has a hollow center.

582
00:31:17,480 --> 00:31:19,400
On the left is the leading position, associated with Fire.

583
00:31:19,400 --> 00:31:21,270
On the right is the position of safeguarding, associated with Heaven.

584
00:31:21,270 --> 00:31:23,820
Remaining position below to be kept in the center.

585
00:31:23,820 --> 00:31:25,680
I've found the formation's core.

586
00:31:42,000 --> 00:31:42,950
Hyah!

587
00:31:48,430 --> 00:31:49,430
Who are you?

588
00:31:49,940 --> 00:31:51,140
Why did you save me?

589
00:31:52,500 --> 00:31:53,990
You aim to shake the stability of Later Ning

590
00:31:53,990 --> 00:31:55,250
and kill Huo Jingheng,

591
00:31:55,520 --> 00:31:57,040
which aligns with my goal.

592
00:31:57,040 --> 00:31:58,440
Why don't we join forces?

593
00:31:59,430 --> 00:32:01,160
What benefits can you offer me?

594
00:32:01,510 --> 00:32:03,130
I am the Crown Prince of Li State.

595
00:32:03,130 --> 00:32:04,600
If you're willing to form an alliance,

596
00:32:04,600 --> 00:32:05,770
I promise

597
00:32:05,800 --> 00:32:07,660
that after Huo Jingheng's death,

598
00:32:07,800 --> 00:32:10,360
Ning State will become a vassal state of Li State,

599
00:32:10,360 --> 00:32:12,860
and I'll crown you as the King of Ning State.

600
00:32:15,350 --> 00:32:16,240
I know

601
00:32:16,560 --> 00:32:18,600
your ambition is not for power and wealth,

602
00:32:18,600 --> 00:32:20,360
but your beloved

603
00:32:20,430 --> 00:32:23,080
will surely appreciate your good intentions

604
00:32:23,280 --> 00:32:25,010
and truly fall in love with you.

605
00:32:25,840 --> 00:32:27,920
But if we are to be allies,

606
00:32:29,190 --> 00:32:33,020
why don't you dare to show your true face?

607
00:32:33,420 --> 00:32:35,450
Well, I've been inconsiderate.

608
00:32:43,340 --> 00:32:46,260
[Yi Qingyun, Crown Prince of Li State]
